CatDescriptText: The musicians listed on the sign behind the saxophone player are: Stan "The Man" Hunter on Organ; Earl Edwards, Tenor Sax; Gil Askey on Trumpet; and Floyd "Wonderful" Smith on Guitar.
TitMainTitle: Danny Turner playing saxophone in front of sign that reads "Another Great Krazy Kris Kolumbo at the Hurricane and His Gentlemen of Swing," at Hurricane Club, 1603 Centre Avenue, Hill District
